data.description: This cozy 1949 Cape Cod with a quarter acre lot is a great starter home or investor. Definity could be a great rental investment. This Family Home has been loved for the last dozen years. HUGE fenced in back yard with a detached larger single car garage . Also an extension off back of garage that is a great work shop or storage shed. 2 bedrooms on first floor and one larger bedroom upstairs. City is putting in new sidewalks and Sewers. This area is up and coming.
